<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>内容来源</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">：“818”项目汽车之家高管专访实录。</span></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">分享嘉宾</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">：</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">邵海峰</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，汽车之家联席总裁。</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">张京宇</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，汽车之家联席总裁。</span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">刘悦</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">，汽车之家副总裁。</span></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">注</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">：笔记侠经主办方和讲者审阅授权发布。</span></p>
